file.name: all-of.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Sample API
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /example:
    get:
      summary: Example
      responses:
          '200':
            description: OK
components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      properties:
        a:
          type: string
    Bar:
      properties:
        b:
          type: number
    Union:
      properties:
        c:
          allOf:
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bar'
    Baz:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/PaginationOptions'
        - type: object
          properties:
            data:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bar'
    PaginationOptions:
      properties:
        cursor:
          type: string
